  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "CNC Machinists",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Setting &amp; operate CNC machines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>操作数控机器（铣床/车床）</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to sets up jigs, fixtures and tooling required for machining process.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>能够设置加工过程所需的夹具</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to write simple programs for CNC Milling machines</li>\n</ul>\n<p>能够为CNC铣床编写简单的程序</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to interpret technical drawing and familiar with drawing symbols</li>\n</ul>\n<p>能够理解技术绘图和熟悉绘图符</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Knowledge and familiarity with machine cutting tools and application of cutting parameters</li>\n</ul>\n<p>熟悉机床切削工具和切削参数的应用</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform in-process inspection of parts and document results when necessary</li>\n</ul>\n<p>必要时执行零件的检查过程和文件结果</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure efficient machine setup, run time and achieve the desired quality expectation of parts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>确保有效的机器设置，运行时间和达到部件质量期望</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Comply with company safety rules and regulations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>遵守公司安全规则</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain good housekeeping practices</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在机器和工作区保持良好的事务管理</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>NITEC/ITE/Technical Certificate in Mechanical/Precision/Tool and Die Engineering or equivalent</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NITEC / ITE / 机械工程文凭或相等文凭</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably with at least 1-2 years of CNC machining experience in Precision Engineering</li>\n</ul>\n<p>至少有1-2年在精密/塑料环境中的CNC加工经验</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to read and interpret blueprints</li>\n</ul>\n<p>能够阅读和理解蓝图</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in CNC routers is highly advantageous</li>\n</ul>\n<p>拥有使用CNC路由器的经验为佳</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>May need to work night shift as required可能需要按要求上夜班</li>\n  <li>No experience, provide training 无经验，提供培训</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates / No experience welcome to apply 应届毕业生/无经验欢迎申请</li>\n  <li>Salary neg. depend on your experience and qualification. 新水面谈， 取决于您的经验和资格。</li>\n</ul>",
